name: Mooi Indie
description: I am grateful to live in the Bandung City, Indonesia.  Despite the hustle and bustle of the socio-political-economy, geographic Bandung has the luxury of being compared to other cities (at least in my opinion).  with a distance that is not too far away, there are so many beautiful and cool places to calm and refresh the mind.  this makes it easier for me if I'm fed up with everyday life in the city.
